Steps on how to create a server using express js from scratch. 

cd to ur folder.
there install the package.json, nodemon and tweak around with the different
parameters.

then install express.

then on a file do this to create a server. 

import express from "express";
const app = express(); 
const PORT = 5000;
app.listen(PORT);
app.get("apis/products" , (request, response) => {
response.send([
{id : "1", name : "aloo", price : 30},
{id : "2", name : "gobi", price : 50},
{id : "3", name : "tamatar", price : 80},
{id : "4", name : "gajar", price : 60},
{id : "5", name : "bhindi", price : 40},
]);
})
